</P>
<P>
The governors reached consensus that central banks in the
region should give due attention to the factor of price
fluctuation in stock markets, real estate and other assets,
besides the traditional price indexes, when making monetary
policies.
</P>
<P>
Dai Xianglong, governor of the People's Bank of China, noted
