</P>
<P>
As part of such efforts, a computer secretariat will be set up
after the meeting, so as to help the EMEAP members share information.
</P>
<P>
The governors also affirmed during the session that a series of
major coordinations and adjustments made by member countries were
positive in coping with the challenge of the recent developments
in regional currency market.
</P>
<P>
So it is fairly appropriate not to consider admitting new
members to the EMEAP at the meeting, since all the bank governors
present regarded the organization as still in its preliminary
stage of development, and this is conducive for the member countries
to have a candid exchange of views.
</P>
<P>
The officials also stressed on the importance of improving
cooperation with the International Monetary Fund and the
