tear gas drifted on to the pitch.
</P>
<P>
The official Antara news agency quoted Nugraha Besoes,
secretary-general of the All Indonesia Soccer Association (PSSI),
as saying that the last 28 minutes of the semifinal between
Bandung Raya and Mitra Surabaya would be played on Saturday
evening, reports said.
