<HEADLINE> South China City Becomes Major Rosin Producer </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NANNING, July 26 (Xinhua) -- The southern Chinese city of
Wuzhou, in Guangxi Province, has become one of the country's major
rosin production centers.
